28#include "qtqrcode.h"
29
30#include <QString>
31
32int discardNegativeNumber(int number) {
33 if (number < 0)
34 return 0;
35 return number;
36}
37
38class QtQrCodeData : public QSharedData
39{
40 friend class QtQrCode;
41private:
42 int width;
43 int version;
44 QByteArray data;
45 QtQrCode::EncodeMode encodeMode;
46 QtQrCode::Proportion proportion;
47 Qt::CaseSensitivity caseSensitivity;
48 QtQrCode::ErrorCorrectionLevel errorCorrectionLevel;
49};
50
51QtQrCode::QtQrCode(int version) : d(new QtQrCodeData)
52{
53 constructorPrivate("", version);
54}
55
56QtQrCode::QtQrCode(QtQrCode::EncodeMode encodeMod) : d(new QtQrCodeData)
57{
58 constructorPrivate("", 0, encodeMod);
59}
60
61QtQrCode::QtQrCode(const QByteArray &data, int version, QtQrCode::EncodeMode encodeMode,
62 QtQrCode::Proportion proportion, Qt::CaseSensitivity caseSensitivity,
63 QtQrCode::ErrorCorrectionLevel errorCorrectionLevel)
64 : d(new QtQrCodeData)
65{
66 constructorPrivate(data, version, encodeMode, proportion,caseSensitivity, errorCorrectionLevel);
67}
68
69void QtQrCode::constructorPrivate(const QByteArray &data, int version, QtQrCode::EncodeMode encodeMode,
70 QtQrCode::Proportion proportion, Qt::CaseSensitivity caseSensitivity,
71 QtQrCode::ErrorCorrectionLevel errorCorrectionLevel)
72{
73 d->width = 0;
74 d->data = data;
75 d->version = (version > 4) ? 0 : discardNegativeNumber(version);
76 d->encodeMode = encodeMode;
77 d->proportion = proportion;
78 d->caseSensitivity = caseSensitivity;
79 d->errorCorrectionLevel = errorCorrectionLevel;
80}
81
82QtQrCode::QtQrCode(const QtQrCode &rhs) : d(rhs.d)
83{
84}
85
86QtQrCode &QtQrCode::operator=(const QtQrCode &rhs)
87{
88 if (this != &rhs)
89 d.operator=(rhs.d);
90 return *this;
91}
92
93QtQrCode::~QtQrCode()
94{
95}
96
97void QtQrCode::encode()
98{
99 if (d->data.isEmpty())
100 return;
101 switch (d->encodeMode) {
102 case StringMode:
103 encodeString();
104 break;
105 case DataMode:
106 encodeData();
107 break;
108 case KanjiMode:
109 encodeSKanji();
110 default:
111 break;
112 }
113}
114
115void QtQrCode::setBaseQrCodeData(QRcode *qrCode)
116{
117 d->width = qrCode->width;
118 d->data.clear();
119 // TODO: Beware it here
120 d->data = (const char *) qrCode->data;
121 QRcode_free(qrCode);
122}
123
124void QtQrCode::encodeData()
125{
126 QRcode *qrCode = NULL;
127 if (d->proportion == MicroProportion) {
128 qrCode = QRcode_encodeDataMQR(d->data.size(), (const unsigned char *) d->data.constData(),
129 d->version, (QRecLevel) d->errorCorrectionLevel);
130 } else {
131 qrCode = QRcode_encodeData(d->data.size(), (const unsigned char *) d->data.constData(),
132 d->version, (QRecLevel) d->errorCorrectionLevel);
133 }
134 if (qrCode == NULL)
135 return;
136
137 setBaseQrCodeData(qrCode);
138}
139
140void QtQrCode::encodeString()
141{
142 QRcode *qrCode = NULL;
143 if (d->proportion == MicroProportion) {
144 qrCode = QRcode_encodeStringMQR(QString(d->data).toStdString().c_str(),
145 d->version, (QRecLevel) d->errorCorrectionLevel,
146 QR_MODE_8, d->caseSensitivity);
147 } else {
148 qrCode = QRcode_encodeString(QString(d->data).toStdString().c_str(),
149 d->version, (QRecLevel) d->errorCorrectionLevel,
150 QR_MODE_8, d->caseSensitivity);
151 }
152 if (qrCode == NULL)
153 return;
154
155 setBaseQrCodeData(qrCode);
156}
157
158void QtQrCode::encodeSKanji()
159{
160 QRcode *qrCode = NULL;
161 if (d->proportion == MicroProportion) {
162 qrCode = QRcode_encodeStringMQR(d->data.constData(), d->version,
163 (QRecLevel) d->errorCorrectionLevel,
164 QR_MODE_KANJI, d->caseSensitivity);
165 } else {
166 qrCode = QRcode_encodeString(d->data.constData(), d->version,
167 (QRecLevel) d->errorCorrectionLevel,
168 QR_MODE_KANJI, d->caseSensitivity);
169 }
170 if (qrCode == NULL)
171 return;
172
173 setBaseQrCodeData(qrCode);
174}

176int QtQrCode::width() const
177{
178 return d->width;
179}
180
181int QtQrCode::version() const
182{
183 return d->version;
184}
185
186void QtQrCode::setVersion(int version)
187{
188 if (version != d->version) {
189 if (version > 4)
190 d->version = 0;
191 else
192 d->version = discardNegativeNumber(version);
193 this->encode();
194 }
195}

197QByteArray QtQrCode::data() const
198{
199 return d->data;
200}
201
202void QtQrCode::setData(const QByteArray &data)
203{
204 if (data != d->data) {
205 d->data = data;
206 this->encode();
207 }
208}

262bool QtQrCode::operator ==(const QtQrCode &other)
263{
264 return d->data == other.d->data;
265}

267bool QtQrCode::operator !=(const QtQrCode &other)
268{
269 return !(*this == other);
